graph TB
    subgraph "Web Platform"
        Browser[React Frontend<br/>TypeScript + shadcn/ui]
        Server[Express.js Server<br/>REST API + WebSocket]
        DB[(PostgreSQL<br/>Device Registry<br/>Search Terms<br/>Audit Logs)]
        Redis[(Redis<br/>Session Store<br/>Cache)]
        Broker[Mosquitto MQTT<br/>Message Broker]
    end
    
    subgraph "Edge Devices"
        Device1[Raspberry Pi 4/5<br/>Camera Framework]
        Device2[NVIDIA Jetson Orin<br/>Camera Framework]
        Device3[macOS Device<br/>Development]
    end
    
    subgraph "AI Services"
        AIService[Groq AI Service<br/>Llama 3.1<br/>Search Processing]
    end
    
    Browser -->|HTTP/REST| Server
    Browser -->|WebSocket| Server
    Server -->|SQL Queries| DB
    Server -->|Session Cache| Redis
    Server -->|HTTP| AIService
    Server <-->|MQTT Pub/Sub| Broker
    Broker <-->|QoS 0-1| Device1
    Broker <-->|QoS 0-1| Device2
    Broker <-->|QoS 0-1| Device3
    
    Device1 -->|Alerts + Snapshots| Broker
    Device2 -->|Alerts + Snapshots| Broker
    Device3 -->|Alerts + Snapshots| Broker
    
    Server -->|Broadcast Events| Browser
    Server -->|Config Updates| Broker
    Server -->|Filter Updates| Broker
    
